','Note: If using an exchange please add the exchange fee to the sent amount. Exchanges usually deduct the fee from the sent amount.'=>'注意：如果使用交易所，请将交易手续费添加到发送金额中。交易所通常会从发送金额中扣除手续费。','Notice'=>'注意','Open QR CODE'=>'打开二维码','Order cancelation timeout'=>'订单取消超时','Order cancelled due to lack of payment.'=>'由于缺乏支付，订单已取消。','Order has been cancelled due to lack of payment. Please don\'t send any payment to the address.'=>'由于缺乏支付，订单已被取消。请不要向该地址发送任何支付。','Order will be cancelled in less than a minute.'=>'订单将在不到一分钟内取消。','Pay'=>'支付','Pay with'=>'支付方式','Payment confirmed'=>'支付已确认','Payment could not be processed, please try again'=>'支付无法处理，请再试一次','Payment detected and confirmed. Customer still need to send'=>'支付已检测并确认。客户仍需发送','Payment error:'=>'支付错误：','Payment method description that the customer will see on your checkout'=>'客户在您的结账页面上将看到的支付方式描述','Please choose a cryptocurrency'=>'请选择一种加密货币','Please renew your subscription'=>'请续订您的订阅','Please renew your subscription on %1$s. You can pay the renewal when you’re ready: %2$s'=>'请在%1$s上续订您的订阅。您可以在准备好时支付续订费用：%2$s。','Please select a Cryptocurrency'=>'请选择一种加密货币','PLEASE SEND'=>'请发送','Processing can take some time depending on the blockchain.'=>'处理时间可能根据区块链的不同而有所不同。','QR Code by default'=>'默认二维码','QR code image size'=>'二维码图像大小','QR Code size'=>'二维码大小','QR Code to show'=>'要显示的二维码','QR Code with value'=>'带有金额的二维码','QR Code without value'=>'无金额的二维码','Refresh converted value'=>'刷新转换值','Select how you want to show the QR Code to the user. Either select a default to show first, or hide one of them.'=>'选择您想如何向用户显示二维码。选择一个默认显示，或隐藏其中一个。','Selects the amount of time the user has to  pay for the order. %1$s When this time is over, order will be marked as "Cancelled" and every paid value will be ignored. %1$s %2$s Notice: %3$s If the user still sends money to the generated address, value will still be redirected to you. %1$s %4$s Warning: %3$s We do not advice more than 1 Hour.'=>'选择用户必须支付订单的时间量。%1$s 当这段时间结束时，订单将被标记为“已取消”，并且每一笔已支付的金额都将被忽略。%1$s %2$s 注意：%3$s 如果用户仍然向生成的地址发送资金，价值仍将被重定向给您。%1$s %4$s 警告：%3$s 我们不建议超过1小时。','Selects the color scheme of the plugin to match your website (Light, Dark and Auto to automatically detect it)'=>'选择插件的配色方案以匹配您的网站（浅色，深色和自动以自动检测）','Service Fee'=>'服务费','Service fee manager'=>'服务费管理器','Set the cryplink service fee you want to charge the costumer. %1$s %2$s Note: %3$s Fee you want to charge your costumers (to cover cryplink\'s fees fully or partially).'=>'设置您想向客户收取的cryplink服务费。%1$s %2$s 注意：%3$s 您想向客户收取的费用（完全或部分覆盖cryplink的费用）。','Show cryplink branding'=>'显示cryplink品牌','Show cryplink logo and credits below the QR code'=>'在二维码下方显示cryplink标志和版权信息','Show crypto logos in checkout'=>'在结账时显示加密货币标志','Show QR Code with value'=>'显示带有金额的二维码','Show QR Code without value'=>'显示无金额的二维码','Show the QR code'=>'显示二维码','Show the QR Code by default'=>'默认显示二维码','So far you sent %1s. Please send a new payment to complete the order, as requested above'=>'到目前为止，您已发送 %1s。请根据上述请求发送新的支付以完成订单','The %1s conversion rate will be adjusted in'=>'%1s 的汇率将在','The cart total must be higher to use this cryptocurrency.'=>'購物車總金額必須更高才能使用這種加密貨幣。','The system will automatically update the conversion value of the invoices (with real-time data), every X minutes. %1$s This feature is helpful whenever a customer takes long time to pay a generated invoice and the selected crypto a volatile coin/token (not stable coin). %1$s %4$s Warning: %3$s Setting this setting to none might create conversion issues, as we advise you to keep it at 5 minutes. %3$s'=>'系统将每X分钟自动更新发票的转换值（使用实时数据）。%1$s 当客户支付生成的发票需要很长时间，且选定的加密货币是波动的币/代币（非稳定币）时，此功能很有帮助。%1$s %4$s 警告：%3$s 将此设置设置为无可能会创建转换问题，因为我们建议您将其保持在5分钟。%3$s','There was an error with the payment. Please try again.'=>'支付时出错。请再试一次。','This controls the title which the user sees during checkout.'=>'这控制了用户在结账时看到的标题。','This order will be valid for %s'=>'此订单将有效期为 %s','This will add an estimation of the blockchain fee to the order value'=>'这将在订单价值中加入一个区块链费用的估算','Time'=>'时间','Title'=>'标题','User sent a payment of'=>'用户已发送支付金额','Value Paid'=>'支付的金额','Value too low, minimum is'=>'价值过低，最低为','Waiting for network confirmation'=>'等待网络确认','Waiting for payment'=>'等待支付','When this setting is enabled, the plugin will mark the order as "completed" then payment is received. %1$s Only for virtual products %2$s.'=>'当此设置启用时，插件将在接收到付款后将订单标记为“已完成”。%1$s 仅适用于虚拟产品%2$s。','WITH AMOUNT'=>'带金额','Your payment has been confirmed!'=>'您的支付已被确认！','Your payment is being processed!'=>'您的支付正在处理中！']];






